{"title":"我向领袖表决心","authors":["杨志和"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":4,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向领袖表决心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军战士　杨志和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永定河的茶花格外红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永定河的水啊格外清；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开宝书语录本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字句句照我心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教我接好革命班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完全彻底为人民；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教我握紧手中枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻警惕有敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花向着太阳转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和我们亲又亲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大领袖一席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士字字刻在心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹起芦笙唱起歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向领袖表决心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪杆笔杆握得紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把牛鬼蛇神全扫清！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}